<item>
            <title>[LU-19373] sanity-lnet test_232: lnetctl lnet unconfigure failed 240 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19373</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/78dc0768-5f14-4dfc-bf72-2314eee77756&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/78dc0768-5f14-4dfc-bf72-2314eee77756&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_232 failed 100% on master with the following error during review-dne-ipv6 and full-dne-ipv6-part1 sessions (99 failures in the past week):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/usr/sbin/lnetctl lnet unconfigure
---
configure:
-     lnet:
      errno: -16
      descr: ! &quot;LNet configure error: Object busy&quot;
...
lnetctl lnet unconfigure failed 240
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4652&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4652&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-570.37.1.el9_6.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4652&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4652&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-570.37.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is nothing of interest on the console logs.&lt;/p&gt;







